#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.ceil.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.ceil"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:1 of
msgid "Return the ceiling of the input, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素返回输入的上界。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:3 of
msgid ""
"The ceil of the scalar `x` is the smallest integer `i`, such that `i >= "
"x`.  It is often denoted as :math:`\\lceil x \\rceil`."
msgstr "\\rceil`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:6 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:8 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有能与输入广播对齐的形状。如果没有"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:13 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:18 of
msgid "**y** -- The ceiling of each element in `x`, with `float` dtype."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 中每个元素的上界，数据类型为 `float`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ceil.ceil:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`floor`, :py:obj:`trunc`, :py:obj:`rint`"
msgstr ""

